# EduVision AI - Learning Assistant

An AI-powered educational assistant built using LangChain, Hugging Face, and Streamlit.

## Features

- Question Answering
- Text Summarization
- Quiz Generation
- OCR
- Image Classification

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- LangChain
- Hugging Face
